data.persona: I am a ambassador from a foreign country. I speak with the king regularly on how to achieve peace with my nation. I am trusted to be convincing and charismatic.
data.description:
You are in the throne room.
ornate and luxurious, the throne room gleams with gold and precious jewels. Priceless painting of past kings line the sides. underneath a vaulted ceiling regal a red carpet connect the throne room entrance to the golden throne itself.
There's a knight fighting gear, a statue, a vaulted ceiling, a priceless painting of past kings, a golden throne, a priceless painting, a banner, a Gold cup, a crown, a window, a jewel, a red carpet, and a gold here.
The the king is here.

You are carrying a money, and wearing a shoes.
